@BGRND{{}}
<p>
When @HI{{@EM{{nishiro}}}} or @HI{{@EM{{niseyo}}}} appears in the final position of a subordinate clause, it carries the expresses a concession.
The meaning is "even if" or "even though".
The literal meaning of @HI{{suru}} in this construction is "to assume".

